\f1\b0\fs28 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\slleading24\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Illustration of growing up in my home that was amazing on so many levels and my parents were great.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Sometimes growing up you don't appreciate all the sacrifice your parents make for you....until you become a parent.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We just celebrated mothers day and fathers day is coming up and so I've been thinking a little about that.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Specially...my dad particularly sacrificed so much for our family. He worked 1st shift, 2nd shift, 3rd shift. He worked in a heat treat plant during the summer which I can't imagine how hot it was in there on the factory line. He always seemed to be willing to work overtime to help my brothers afford a sport we wanted to do.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And I say all of this not as a way to suck up to my dad...but point out my own hypocrisy with him because honestly as I look back...he didn't ask a lot of me. \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li1440\fi-1440\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}He didn't ask me to work a job in high school\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}He didn't ask me to get straight A's...I was lucky to get C's honestly.\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}He didn't ask me to do much...\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}Just take out the trash every now and then...clean up my room...maybe do the dishes (we did have a dishwasher...they were called Nic and Mic)\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1120\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Which is important to today's topic because if you're a parent you're going to be able to relate...\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1120\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I HATED DOING THOSE THINGS!!!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1120\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I mean you would have thought my dad was asking me to work 8 hour days taking out the trash not 30 seconds...but in the moment i couldn't stand it.\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
