\f0\b \cf3 TRANSITION:  We are often SO grateful for those who sacrifice for us...and yet when it comes time to sacrifice for others there is this pull in all of us...there is this disconnect that happens..\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf0 \
\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 WE
\f1\b0\fs28 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And I get it because I have the same tension. I want people to sacrifice for me but when it comes time for me to sacrifice...well I can come up with 100 reasons why I can't or couldn't...or sometimes I'm so good at talking myself out of sacrifice I can convince myself I even "shouldn't"\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But that is NOT who we are called to be\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We are called to be generous and giving and sacrificial.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is why our last core value that we are talking about is the most important one...\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}In fact if you don't adopt this one you'll never step into the other 4...it's that important.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}it is the foundation that supports all other values we have as a church and it's this...\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li1440\fi-1440\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1\cf4 {\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}Core Value #5 - We can't PLAN a move of God but we will PREPARE for one\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}Core Value #4 - We will be OWNERS and not RENTERS\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
